{
  "stem": "3040.5",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, most of the dreams are that I lived in fear.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that awesome, awesome fear of the Germans.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, it's-- it is-- you cannot really-- I cannot express this in-- in words to explain what that fear means.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I think people who didn't go through it, who didn't live through it, cannot imagine what that means.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because it is an apathy combined with fear.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "On the one hand, I don't care, because I lost everybody already.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What-- what does it-- what do I care what will happen to me?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and on the other hand, it's this powerful fear-- what will happen to me?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's contradictory.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I also wanted to mention, in my activities now, I'm very much involved with the Jewish Center, of which I'm not only a member, but I'm also a neighbor.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's the-- called the Jewish [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the Jewish Community Center of West Hempstead.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I also-- I-- I am very much involved in the-- in-- in our program for remembering the Shoah.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Every year, around Yom HaShoah, which is the 27th day of Nisan, a few days, five days after Pesach, most of the congregations have some programs to remember the Shoah.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I and Norbert Friedman are very-- are the chairpersons in that function of remembering the Shoah.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we're preparing, every year, a different kind of a program to interest not only the members of the congregation, but also the community.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We invite the clergy to come, and they do come.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We invite, sometimes, politicians to come.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we are very much involved.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When time comes, around April time, Norbert and I are very much involved in preparing programs.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we try to be imaginative, not repetitious.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
